  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nThis is from a test mainnet node subscribing to all subnets.\r\n\r\nAfter #5350 after a while when there are 30% of dropped attestations, 100% of sync committee messages and sync contribution and proofs are dropped since then and node is not able to recover (after I restart it gets back to 0% drop)\r\n\r\n<img width=\"804\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-04-09 at 17 27 44\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/230767563-d85bbd70-6799-467b-b767-591fe79c2002.png\">\r\n\r\nwhile beacon_attestation topic is consistently at around its max size\r\n\r\n<img width=\"791\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-04-09 at 17 29 49\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/230767647-2c7effc5-69a7-4b13-9b09-31a575bb7fcc.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nRight now when adding a gossip message, we delete exactly 1 gossip message.\r\nAs we have to drop 30% - 40% of attestations anyway, how about drop 30% - 40% of attestation messages when queue is at max size to allow the node to recover @dapplion ?",
